Use the standard library
This is how to tri of n:
   Remember that result is [1, 3]
   Remember that i is 3
   Do this n times:
      When i is more than n, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when
      When remainder of i and 2 is 1, then:
         Add result to quotient of (tofloat of (sum of i and 1)) and 2
      But, if not:
         Add result to product of (tofloat of i) and (tofloat of i)
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is result
Now you know